dmca.title: Akamedia claims unauthorized exposure of Janet Jackson videos
dmca.body:
Ladies and Gentlemen,

I, CEO of Akamedia, act as the official representative of the producer (the "Owner") of the following video material (the "Video Material"):
Janet Jackson sunbathing in an hotel in Miami, playing bongo on her chest and her bottom Akamedia Ref: # 11846 and #1151
